commit.message:
Fix auth response formats to match API models

- Register: return {success, user_id} instead of {message, username, user_id}
- Login: return {success, token, user_id} instead of {message, token, user_id, username}
- Logout: return {success, message} instead of {message}

This ensures responses match the Pydantic models and pass validation.

